- Synced all 115 sites from Google Sheets (was 75)
- Added missing Shopify stores: menoquil.com, phenocal.com, provasil.com
- Added 20 Shopify 301 redirect domains with redirect validation
- Added SEO/PBN sites: memoforce.online, prostastream.online, etc
- Added WordPress backup/staging sites
- Integrated product priority rankings from revenue sheet
