From: Amit Jain <8amitjain@gmail.com>
Date: Fri, 17 Apr 2026 17:13:34 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] Per-site PDF reports with core QA checks, no ecommerce

Rewrote cron.py to generate individual PDF reports per site
instead of one combined report. Each PDF covers broken images,
broken navigation links, SSL health, page performance, meta/SEO
basics, and content quality. Removed all ecommerce-specific checks
(CTA, cart, checkout). Problem-site PDFs are posted as threaded
replies in Slack #automated-qc. Increased workflow timeout to 90min
for 74-site audit with per-site PDF generation.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
